Overview

A scalable, production-ready iOS healthcare system built with UIKit-programmatically, implementing MVVM-C (Model-View-ViewModel-Coordinator) 
pattern with Clean Architecture principles. The module manages patient profiles, appointments, and vital signs with 
emphasis on testability, maintainability, and HIPAA-conscious development practices.

Features
Core Functionality

Patient Profile Management: Comprehensive patient information display
Appointments: List view with filtering (upcoming/past) and detailed view
Vitals Tracking: Real-time vital signs monitoring with status indicators
Navigation: Coordinator-based navigation for complete decoupling

Technical Features

✅ MVVM-C Architecture with Clean Architecture layering
✅ Combine framework for reactive state management
✅ Protocol-based dependency injection
✅ Repository pattern for data abstraction
✅ Programmatic Auto Layout
✅ Dark Mode support
✅ Dynamic Type & VoiceOver accessibility
✅ Comprehensive unit tests
✅ HIPAA-conscious data handling
✅ Extension in clean Architecture principles
